<% layout("./listing/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-5">
                    <h1 class="text-center mb-4 text-gradient">Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted text-center mb-5">Last updated: December 2024</p>

                    <div class="privacy-content">
                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved me-2 text-primary"></i>1. Introduction</h4>
                            <p>Welcome to TravelSathi. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services.</p>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-database me-2 text-primary"></i>2. Information We Collect</h4>
                            <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and profile information when you register</li>
                                <li><strong>Listing Information:</strong> Property details, images, location data, and pricing information</li>
                                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on our platform</li>
                                <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Processed securely through our payment partners</li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye me-2 text-primary"></i>3. How We Use Your Information</h4>
                            <p>We use your information to:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
                                <li>Process bookings and transactions</li>
                                <li>Communicate with you about your account and listings</li>
                                <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
                                <li>Send promotional emails (with your consent)</li>
                                <li>Prevent fraud and ensure security</li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-share-nodes me-2 text-primary"></i>4. Information Sharing</h4>
                            <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Service providers who assist our operations</li>
                                <li>Payment processors for secure transactions</li>
                                <li>Law enforcement when required by law</li>
                                <li>Other users only when necessary for bookings (limited information)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-lock me-2 text-primary"></i>5. Data Security</h4>
                            <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. This includes encryption, secure servers, and regular security assessments.</p>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-user-check me-2 text-primary"></i>6. Your Rights</h4>
                            <p>You have the right to:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Access your personal information</li>
                                <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
                                <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                                <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
                                <li>Export your data</li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-cookie-bite me-2 text-primary"></i>7. Cookies</h4>
                            <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze site traffic, and personalize content. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
                        </section>

                        <section class="mb-4">
                            <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope me-2 text-primary"></i>8. Contact Us</h4>
                            <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
                            <p><strong>Email:</strong> princekumar46399@gmail.com</p>
                            <p><strong>Website:</strong> www.wanderlust.com</p>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }
    .privacy-content h4 {
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .privacy-content p, .privacy-content li {
        color: #4a5568;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .privacy-content ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    .privacy-content li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>
